title: Flying Star Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Restaurant chain in New Mexico. Serving breakfast all day, lunch, and dinner. Offers a few ovo lacto vegetarian options. Substitute any egg dish with tofu, and make it vegan by omitting cheese. Despite the fact that they do serve meat, they do only serve American Humane Certified meat. Uses organic ingredients and local products. You can bring your dog to the pet-io. Has Wi-Fi.
